var book = {
	"name": "Lamentations",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20312A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20312A\"></sup>lonely sits the cityThat was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20312B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20312B\"></sup>full of people!She has become like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20312C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20312C\"></sup>widowWho was <i>once</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20312D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20312D\"></sup>great among the nations!She who was a princess among the provincesHas become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20312E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20312E\"></sup>forced laborer!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20313F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20313F\"></sup>weeps bitterly in the nightAnd her tears are on her cheeks;She has none to comfort herAmong all her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20313G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20313G\"></sup>lovers.All her friends have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20313H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20313H\"></sup>dealt treacherously with her;They have become her enemies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20314I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20314I\"></sup>Judah has gone into exile under afflictionAnd under harsh servitude;She dwells <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20314J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20314J\"></sup>among the nations,<i>But</i> she has found no rest;All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20314K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20314K\"></sup>her pursuers have overtaken herIn the midst of distress.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The roads of Zion are in mourningBecause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20315L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20315L\"></sup>no one comes to the appointed feasts.All her gates are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20315M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20315M\"></sup>desolate;Her priests are groaning,Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20315N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20315N\"></sup>virgins are afflicted,And she herself is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20315O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20315O\"></sup>bitter.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Her adversaries have become her masters,Her enemies prosper;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20316P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20316P\"></sup>caused her griefBecause of the multitude of her transgressions;Her little ones have gone awayAs captives before the adversary.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>All her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20317Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20317Q\"></sup>majestyHas departed from the daughter of Zion;Her princes have become like deerThat have found no pasture;And they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20317R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20317R\"></sup>fled without strengthBefore the pursuer.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In the days of her affliction and homelessness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20318S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20318S\"></sup>Jerusalem remembers all her precious thingsThat were from the days of old,When her people fell into the hand of the adversaryAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20318T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20318T\"></sup>no one helped her.The adversaries saw her,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20318U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20318U\"></sup>mocked at her ruin.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jerusalem sinned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20319V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20319V\"></sup>greatly,Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20319W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20319W\"></sup>she has become an unclean thing.All who honored her despise herBecause they have seen her nakedness;Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20319X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20319X\"></sup>she herself groans and turns away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320Y\"></sup>uncleanness was in her skirts;She did not consider her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320Z\"></sup>future.Therefore she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320AA\"></sup>fallen astonishingly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320AB\"></sup>She has no comforter.“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320AC\"></sup>See, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, my affliction,For the enemy has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20320AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20320AD\"></sup>magnified himself!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The adversary has stretched out his handOver all her precious things,For she has seen the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20321AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20321AE\"></sup>nations enter her sanctuary,The ones whom You commandedThat they should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20321AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20321AF\"></sup>not enter into Your congregation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All her people groan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20322AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20322AG\"></sup>seeking bread;They have given their precious things for foodTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20322AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20322AH\"></sup>restore their lives themselves.“See, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and look,For I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20322AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20322AI\"></sup>despised.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20323AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20323AJ\"></sup>it nothing to all you who pass this way?Look and see if there is any pain like my painWhich was severely dealt out to me,Which the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20323AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20323AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> inflicted on the day of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20323AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20323AL\"></sup>fierce anger.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“From on high He sent fire into my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20324AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20324AM\"></sup>bones,And it prevailed <i>over them</i>.He has spread a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20324AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20324AN\"></sup>net for my feet;He has turned me back;He has made me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20324AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20324AO\"></sup>desolate,Faint all day long.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20325AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20325AP\"></sup>yoke of my transgressions is bound;By His hand they are knit together.They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20325AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20325AQ\"></sup>come upon my neck;He has made my strength fail.The Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20325AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20325AR\"></sup>has given me into the handsOf <i>those against whom</i> I am not able to stand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20326AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20326AS\"></sup>Lord has rejected all my strong menIn my midst;He has called an appointed time against meTo crush my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20326AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20326AT\"></sup>young men;The Lord has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20326AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20326AU\"></sup>trodden <i>as in</i> a wine pressThe virgin daughter of Judah.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For these things I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20327AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20327AV\"></sup>weep;My eyes run down with water;Because far from me is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20327AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20327AW\"></sup>comforter,One who restores my soul.My children are desolateBecause the enemy has prevailed.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Zion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20328AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20328AX\"></sup>stretches out her hands;There is no one to comfort her;The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20328AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20328AY\"></sup>commanded concerning JacobThat the ones round about him should be his adversaries;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20328AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20328AZ\"></sup>Jerusalem has become an unclean thing among them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20329BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20329BA\"></sup>righteous;For I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20329BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20329BB\"></sup>rebelled against His command;Hear now, all peoples,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20329BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20329BC\"></sup>behold my pain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20329BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20329BD\"></sup>My virgins and my young menHave gone into captivity.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20330BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20330BE\"></sup>called to my lovers, <i>but</i> they deceived me;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20330BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20330BF\"></sup>priests and my elders perished in the cityWhile they sought food to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20330BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20330BG\"></sup>restore their strength themselves.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“See, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for I am in distress;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20331BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20331BH\"></sup>spirit is greatly troubled;My heart is overturned within me,For I have been very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20331BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20331BI\"></sup>rebellious.In the street the sword slays;In the house it is like death.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“They have heard that I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20332BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20332BJ\"></sup>groan;There is no one to comfort me;All my enemies have heard of my calamity;They are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20332BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20332BK\"></sup>glad that You have done <i>it</i>.Oh, that You would bring the day which You have proclaimed,That they may become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20332BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20332BL\"></sup>like me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Let all their wickedness come before You;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20333BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20333BM\"></sup>deal with them as You have dealt with meFor all my transgressions;For my groans are many and my heart is faint.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>How the Lord has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20334A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20334A\"></sup>covered the daughter of ZionWith a cloud in His anger!He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20334B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20334B\"></sup>cast from heaven to earthThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20334C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20334C\"></sup>glory of Israel,And has not remembered His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20334D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20334D\"></sup>footstoolIn the day of His anger.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The Lord has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20335E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20335E\"></sup>swallowed up; He has not sparedAll the habitations of Jacob.In His wrath He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20335F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20335F\"></sup>thrown downThe strongholds of the daughter of Judah;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20335G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20335G\"></sup>brought <i>them</i> down to the ground;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20335H\"></sup>profaned the kingdom and its princes.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In fierce anger He has cut offAll the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20336I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20336I\"></sup>strength of Israel;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20336J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20336J\"></sup>drawn back His right handFrom before the enemy.And He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20336K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20336K\"></sup>burned in Jacob like a flaming fireConsuming round about.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He has bent His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20337L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20337L\"></sup>bow like an enemy;He has set His right hand like an adversaryAnd slain all that were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20337M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20337M\"></sup>pleasant to the eye;In the tent of the daughter of ZionHe has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20337N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20337N\"></sup>poured out His wrath like fire.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Lord has become like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20338O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20338O\"></sup>enemy.He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20338P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20338P\"></sup>swallowed up Israel;He has swallowed up all its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20338Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20338Q\"></sup>palaces,He has destroyed its strongholdsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20338R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20338R\"></sup>multiplied in the daughter of JudahMourning and moaning.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And He has violently treated His tabernacle like a garden <i>booth</i>;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20339S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20339S\"></sup>destroyed His appointed meeting place.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20339T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20339T\"></sup>caused to be forgottenThe appointed feast and sabbath in Zion,And He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20339U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20339U\"></sup>despised king and priestIn the indignation of His anger.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The Lord has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20340V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20340V\"></sup>rejected His altar,He has abandoned His sanctuary;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20340W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20340W\"></sup>has delivered into the hand of the enemyThe walls of her palaces.They have made a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20340X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20340X\"></sup>noise in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>As in the day of an appointed feast.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> determined to destroyThe wall of the daughter of Zion.He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20341Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20341Y\"></sup>stretched out a line,He has not restrained His hand from destroying,And He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20341Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20341Z\"></sup>caused rampart and wall to lament;They have languished together.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20342AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20342AA\"></sup>gates have sunk into the ground,He has destroyed and broken her bars.Her king and her princes are among the nations;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20342AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20342AB\"></sup>law is no more.Also, her prophets find<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20342AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20342AC\"></sup>No vision from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The elders of the daughter of Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20343AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20343AD\"></sup>Sit on the ground, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20343AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20343AE\"></sup>are silent.They have thrown <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20343AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20343AF\"></sup>dust on their heads;They have girded themselves with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20343AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20343AG\"></sup>sackcloth.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20343AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20343AH\"></sup>virgins of JerusalemHave bowed their heads to the ground.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20344AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20344AI\"></sup>eyes fail because of tears,My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20344AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20344AJ\"></sup>spirit is greatly troubled;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20344AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20344AK\"></sup>heart is poured out on the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20344AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20344AL\"></sup>Because of the destruction of the daughter of my people,When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20344AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20344AM\"></sup>little ones and infants faintIn the streets of the city.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They say to their mothers,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20345AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20345AN\"></sup>Where is grain and wine?”As they faint like a wounded manIn the streets of the city,As their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20345AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20345AO\"></sup>life is poured outOn their mothers’ bosom.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>How shall I admonish you?To what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20346AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20346AP\"></sup>shall I compare you,O daughter of Jerusalem?To what shall I liken you as I comfort you,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20346AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20346AQ\"></sup>virgin daughter of Zion?For your ruin is as vast as the sea;Who can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20346AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20346AR\"></sup>heal you?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20347AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20347AS\"></sup>prophets have seen for youFalse and foolish <i>visions</i>;And they have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20347AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20347AT\"></sup>exposed your iniquitySo as to restore you from captivity,But they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20347AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20347AU\"></sup>seen for you false and misleading oracles.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All who pass along the way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20348AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20348AV\"></sup>Clap their hands <i>in derision</i> at you;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20348AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20348AW\"></sup>hiss and shake their headsAt the daughter of Jerusalem,“Is this the city of which they said,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20348AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20348AX\"></sup>The perfection of beauty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20348AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20348AY\"></sup>A joy to all the earth’?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>All <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20349AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20349AZ\"></sup>your enemiesHave opened their mouths wide against you;They hiss and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20349BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20349BA\"></sup>gnash <i>their</i> teeth.They say, “We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20349BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20349BB\"></sup>swallowed <i>her</i> up!Surely this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20349BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20349BC\"></sup>day for which we waited;We have reached <i>it</i>, we have seen <i>it</i>.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20350BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20350BD\"></sup>done what He purposed;He has accomplished His wordWhich He commanded from days of old.He has thrown down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20350BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20350BE\"></sup>without sparing,And He has caused the enemy to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20350BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20350BF\"></sup>rejoice over you;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20350BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20350BG\"></sup>exalted the might of your adversaries.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20351BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20351BH\"></sup>heart cried out to the Lord,“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20351BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20351BI\"></sup>wall of the daughter of Zion,Let <i>your</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20351BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20351BJ\"></sup>tears run down like a river day and night;Give yourself no relief,Let your eyes have no rest.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Arise, cry aloud in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20352BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20352BK\"></sup>nightAt the beginning of the night watches;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20352BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20352BL\"></sup>Pour out your heart like waterBefore the presence of the Lord;Lift up your hands to HimFor the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20352BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20352BM\"></sup>life of your little onesWho are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20352BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20352BN\"></sup>faint because of hungerAt the head of every street.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>See, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and look!With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20353BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20353BO\"></sup>whom have You dealt thus?Should women <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20353BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20353BP\"></sup>eat their offspring,The little ones who were born healthy?Should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20353BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20353BQ\"></sup>priest and prophet be slainIn the sanctuary of the Lord?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>On the ground in the streetsLie <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20354BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20354BR\"></sup>young and old;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20354BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20354BS\"></sup>virgins and my young menHave fallen by the sword.You have slain <i>them</i> in the day of Your anger,You have slaughtered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20354BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20354BT\"></sup>not sparing.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You called as in the day of an appointed feastMy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20355BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20355BU\"></sup>terrors on every side;And there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20355BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20355BV\"></sup>no one who escaped or survivedIn the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> anger.Those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20355BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20355BW\"></sup>whom I bore and reared,My enemy annihilated them."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>I am the man who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20356A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20356A\"></sup>seen afflictionBecause of the rod of His wrath.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He has driven me and made me walkIn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20357B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20357B\"></sup>darkness and not in light.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Surely against me He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20358C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20358C\"></sup>turned His handRepeatedly all the day.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He has caused my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20359D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20359D\"></sup>flesh and my skin to waste away,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20359E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20359E\"></sup>broken my bones.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20360F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20360F\"></sup>besieged and encompassed me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20360G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20360G\"></sup>bitterness and hardship.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20361H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20361H\"></sup>dark places He has made me dwell,Like those who have long been dead.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20362I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20362I\"></sup>walled me in so that I cannot go out;He has made my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20362J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20362J\"></sup>chain heavy.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Even when I cry out and call for help,He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20363K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20363K\"></sup>shuts out my prayer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20364L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20364L\"></sup>blocked my ways with hewn stone;He has made my paths crooked.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He is to me like a bear lying in wait,<i>Like</i> a lion in secret places.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He has turned aside my ways and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20366M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20366M\"></sup>torn me to pieces;He has made me desolate.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20367N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20367N\"></sup>bent His bowAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20367O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20367O\"></sup>set me as a target for the arrow.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He made the arrows of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20368P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20368P\"></sup>quiverTo enter into my inward parts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20369Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20369Q\"></sup>laughingstock to all my people,Their <i>mocking</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20369R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20369R\"></sup>song all the day.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20370S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20370S\"></sup>filled me with bitterness,He has made me drunk with wormwood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20371T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20371T\"></sup>broken my teeth with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20371U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20371U\"></sup>gravel;He has made me cower in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20371V\"></sup>dust.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My soul has been rejected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20372W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20372W\"></sup>from peace;I have forgotten happiness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So I say, “My strength has perished,And <i>so has</i> my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20373X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20373X\"></sup>hope from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Remember my affliction and my wandering, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20374Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20374Y\"></sup>wormwood and bitterness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20375Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20375Z\"></sup>my soul remembersAnd is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20375AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20375AA\"></sup>bowed down within me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>This I recall to my mind,Therefore I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20376AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20376AB\"></sup>hope.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20377AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20377AC\"></sup>lovingkindnesses indeed never cease,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20377AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20377AD\"></sup>For His compassions never fail.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><i>They</i> are new <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20378AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20378AE\"></sup>every morning;Great is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20378AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20378AF\"></sup>Your faithfulness.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20379AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20379AG\"></sup>portion,” says my soul,“Therefore I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20379AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20379AH\"></sup>have hope in Him.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is good to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20380AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20380AI\"></sup>wait for Him,To the person who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20380AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20380AJ\"></sup>seeks Him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><i>It is</i> good that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20381AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20381AK\"></sup>waits silentlyFor the salvation of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><i>It is</i> good for a man that he should bearThe yoke in his youth.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20383AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20383AL\"></sup>sit alone and be silentSince He has laid <i>it</i> on him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Let him put his mouth in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20384AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20384AM\"></sup>dust,Perhaps there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20384AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20384AN\"></sup>hope.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Let him give his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20385AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20385AO\"></sup>cheek to the smiter,Let him be filled with reproach.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For the Lord will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20386AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20386AP\"></sup>not reject forever,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For if He causes grief,Then He will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20387AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20387AQ\"></sup>compassionAccording to His abundant lovingkindness.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20388AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20388AR\"></sup>does not afflict willinglyOr grieve the sons of men.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>To crush under His feetAll the prisoners of the land,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>To deprive a man of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20390AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20390AS\"></sup>justiceIn the presence of the Most High,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20391AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20391AT\"></sup>defraud a man in his lawsuit—Of these things the Lord does not approve.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Who is there who speaks and it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20392AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20392AU\"></sup>comes to pass,Unless the Lord has commanded <i>it</i>?",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><i>Is it</i> not from the mouth of the Most HighThat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20393AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20393AV\"></sup>both good and ill go forth?",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Why should <i>any</i> living mortal, or <i>any</i> man,Offer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20394AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20394AW\"></sup>complaint in view of his sins?",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20395AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20395AX\"></sup>examine and probe our ways,And let us return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20396AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20396AY\"></sup>lift up our heart and handsToward God in heaven;",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20397AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20397AZ\"></sup>transgressed and rebelled,You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20397BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20397BA\"></sup>not pardoned.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>You have covered <i>Yourself</i> with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20398BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20398BB\"></sup>angerAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20398BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20398BC\"></sup>pursued us;You have slain <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20398BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20398BD\"></sup>have not spared.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20399BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20399BE\"></sup>covered Yourself with a cloudSo that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20399BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20399BF\"></sup>no prayer can pass through.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><i>You have made us mere</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20400BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20400BG\"></sup>offscouring and refuseIn the midst of the peoples.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>All our enemies have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20401BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20401BH\"></sup>opened their mouths against us.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20402BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20402BI\"></sup>Panic and pitfall have befallen us,Devastation and destruction;",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20403BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20403BJ\"></sup>eyes run down with streams of waterBecause of the destruction of the daughter of my people.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>My eyes pour down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20404BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20404BK\"></sup>unceasingly,Without stopping,",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Until the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20405BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20405BL\"></sup>looks downAnd sees from heaven.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>My eyes bring pain to my soulBecause of all the daughters of my city.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>My enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20407BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20407BM\"></sup>without causeHunted me down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20407BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20407BN\"></sup>like a bird;",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>They have silenced me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20408BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20408BO\"></sup>in the pitAnd have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20408BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20408BP\"></sup>placed a stone on me.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Waters flowed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20409BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20409BQ\"></sup>over my head;I said, “I am cut off!”",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20410BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20410BR\"></sup>called on Your name, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Out of the lowest pit.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20411BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20411BS\"></sup>heard my voice,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20411BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20411BT\"></sup>Do not hide Your ear from my <i>prayer for</i> relief,From my cry for help.”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20412BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20412BU\"></sup>drew near when I called on You;You said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20412BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20412BV\"></sup>Do not fear!”",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>O Lord, You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20413BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20413BW\"></sup>have pleaded my soul’s cause;You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20413BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20413BX\"></sup>redeemed my life.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20414BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20414BY\"></sup>seen my oppression;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20414BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20414BZ\"></sup>Judge my case.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>You have seen all their vengeance,All their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20415CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20415CA\"></sup>schemes against me.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>You have heard their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20416CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20416CB\"></sup>reproach, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,All their schemes against me.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20417CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20417CC\"></sup>lips of my assailants and their whispering<i>Are</i> against me all day long.",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>Look on their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20418CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20418CD\"></sup>sitting and their rising;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20418CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20418CE\"></sup>I am their mocking song.",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20419CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20419CF\"></sup>recompense them, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,According to the work of their hands.",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>You will give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20420CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20420CG\"></sup>hardness of heart,Your curse will be on them.",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20421CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20421CH\"></sup>pursue them in anger and destroy themFrom under the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20421CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20421CI\"></sup>heavens of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20422A\"></sup>dark the gold has become,<i>How</i> the pure gold has changed!The sacred stones are poured outAt the corner of every street.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The precious sons of Zion,Weighed against fine gold,How they are regarded as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20423B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20423B\"></sup>earthen jars,The work of a potter’s hands!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20424C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20424C\"></sup>jackals offer the breast,They nurse their young;<i>But</i> the daughter of my people has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20424D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20424D\"></sup>cruelLike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20424E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20424E\"></sup>ostriches in the wilderness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20425F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20425F\"></sup>tongue of the infant cleavesTo the roof of its mouth because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20425G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20425G\"></sup>thirst;The little ones <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20425H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20425H\"></sup>ask for bread,<i>But</i> no one breaks <i>it</i> for them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who ate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20426I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20426I\"></sup>delicaciesAre desolate in the streets;Those reared in purpleEmbrace ash pits.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For the iniquity of the daughter of my peopleIs greater than the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20427J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20427J\"></sup>sin of Sodom,Which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20427K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20427K\"></sup>overthrown as in a moment,And no hands were turned toward her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Her consecrated ones were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20428L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20428L\"></sup>purer than snow,They were whiter than milk;They were more ruddy <i>in</i> body than corals,Their polishing <i>was like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20428M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20428M\"></sup>lapis lazuli.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their appearance is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20429N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20429N\"></sup>blacker than soot,They are not recognized in the streets;Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20429O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20429O\"></sup>skin is shriveled on their bones,It is withered, it has become like wood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Better are those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20430P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20430P\"></sup>slain with the swordThan those slain with hunger;For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20430Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20430Q\"></sup>pine away, being strickenFor lack of the fruits of the field.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The hands of compassionate women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20431R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20431R\"></sup>Boiled their own children;They became <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20431S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20431S\"></sup>food for themBecause of the destruction of the daughter of my people.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20432T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20432T\"></sup>accomplished His wrath,He has poured out His fierce anger;And He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20432U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20432U\"></sup>kindled a fire in ZionWhich has consumed its foundations.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The kings of the earth did not believe,Nor <i>did</i> any of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20433V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20433V\"></sup>the inhabitants of the world,That the adversary and the enemyCould <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20433W\"></sup>enter the gates of Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Because of the sins of her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20434X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20434X\"></sup>prophets<i>And</i> the iniquities of her priests,Who have shed in her midstThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20434Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20434Y\"></sup>blood of the righteous;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They wandered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20435Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20435Z\"></sup>blind, in the streets;They were defiled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20435AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20435AA\"></sup>bloodSo that no one could touch their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20435AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20435AB\"></sup>garments.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Depart! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20436AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20436AC\"></sup>Unclean!” they cried of themselves.“Depart, depart, do not touch!”So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20436AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20436AD\"></sup>fled and wandered;<i>Men</i> among the nations said,“They shall not continue to dwell <i>with us</i>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has scattered them,He will not continue to regard them;They did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20437AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20437AE\"></sup>honor the priests,They did not favor the elders.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Yet our eyes failed,<i>Looking</i> for help was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20438AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20438AF\"></sup>useless;In our watching we have watchedFor a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20438AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20438AG\"></sup>nation that could not save.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20439AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20439AH\"></sup>hunted our stepsSo that we could not walk in our streets;Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20439AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20439AI\"></sup>end drew near,Our days were finishedFor our end had come.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Our pursuers were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20440AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20440AJ\"></sup>swifterThan the eagles of the sky;They chased us on the mountains,They waited in ambush for us in the wilderness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20441AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20441AK\"></sup>breath of our nostrils, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20441AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20441AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> anointed,Was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20441AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20441AM\"></sup>captured in their pits,Of whom we had said, “Under his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20441AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20441AN\"></sup>shadowWe shall live among the nations.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Rejoice and be glad, O daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20442AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20442AO\"></sup>Edom,Who dwells in the land of Uz;<i>But</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20442AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20442AP\"></sup>cup will come around to you as well,You will become drunk and make yourself naked.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><i>The punishment</i> of your iniquity has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20443AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20443AQ\"></sup>completed, O daughter of Zion;He will exile you no longer.<i>But</i> He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20443AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20443AR\"></sup>will punish your iniquity, O daughter of Edom;He will expose your sins!"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Remember, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, what has befallen us;Look, and see our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20444A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20444A\"></sup>reproach!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Our inheritance has been turned over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20445B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20445B\"></sup>strangers,Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20445C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20445C\"></sup>houses to aliens.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We have become orphans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20446D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20446D\"></sup>without a father,Our mothers are like widows.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We have to pay for our drinking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20447E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20447E\"></sup>water,Our wood comes <i>to us</i> at a price.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Our pursuers are at our necks;We are worn out, there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20448F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20448F\"></sup>no rest for us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We have submitted to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20449G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20449G\"></sup>Egypt <i>and</i> Assyria to get enough bread.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20450H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20450H\"></sup>fathers sinned, <i>and</i> are no more;It is we who have borne their iniquities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20451I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20451I\"></sup>Slaves rule over us;There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20451J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20451J\"></sup>no one to deliver us from their hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We get our bread at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20452K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20452K\"></sup>risk of our livesBecause of the sword in the wilderness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Our skin has become as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20453L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20453L\"></sup>hot as an oven,Because of the burning heat of famine.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They ravished the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20454M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20454M\"></sup>women in Zion,The virgins in the cities of Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Princes were hung by their hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20455N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20455N\"></sup>Elders were not respected.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Young men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20456O\"></sup>worked at the grinding mill,And youths <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20456P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20456P\"></sup>stumbled under <i>loads</i> of wood.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Elders are gone from the gate,Young men from their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20457Q\"></sup>music.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The joy of our hearts has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20458R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20458R\"></sup>ceased;Our dancing has been turned into mourning.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20459S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20459S\"></sup>crown has fallen from our head;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20459T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20459T\"></sup>Woe to us, for we have sinned!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because of this our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20460U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20460U\"></sup>heart is faint,Because of these things our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20460V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20460V\"></sup>eyes are dim;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20461W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20461W\"></sup>Mount Zion which lies desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20461X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20461X\"></sup>Foxes prowl in it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20462Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20462Y\"></sup>You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, rule forever;Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20462Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20462Z\"></sup>throne is from generation to generation.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Why do You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20463AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20463AA\"></sup>forget us forever?Why do You forsake us so long?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20464AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20464AB\"></sup>Restore us to You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that we may be restored;Renew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20464AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20464AC\"></sup>our days as of old,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Unless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20465AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20465AD\"></sup>You have utterly rejected us<i>And</i> are exceedingly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-20465AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-20465AE\"></sup>angry with us."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;